安装jenkins 下载war包并启动，浏览器输入地址端口为启动时输入的 插件安装 ：manage jenkins -&gt; manage plugin 远程操作： ​ 配置依赖 &lt;!-- https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/com.offbytwo.jenkins/jenkins-client --&gt; com.offbytwo.jenkins jenkins-client 0.3.8 参考代码： 123456789101112131415161718192021222324252627282930313233343536373839404142434445464748495051525354555657585960616263646566676869707172737475767778798081828384858687888990919293949596979899100101102103104105106107108109110111 // 连接 Jenkins JenkinsServer jenkins = new JenkinsServer(new URI(&quot;http://your-jenkins-url&quot;), &quot;your-username&quot;, &quot;your-api-token&quot;); // Job 名称 String jobName = &quot;complex-project-deployment&quot;; // Pipeline XML 配置 String jobConfigXml = &quot;&lt;flow-definition plugin=\&quot;workflow-job@2.42\&quot;&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;actions/&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;description&gt;A complete example for project deployment&lt;/description&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;keepDependencies&gt;false&lt;/keepDependencies&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;properties&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;hudson.model.ParametersDefinitionProperty&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;parameterDefinitions&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;name&gt;BRANCH&lt;/name&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;description&gt;Branch to build&lt;/description&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;defaultValue&gt;main&lt;/defaultValue&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;/hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;name&gt;ENVIRONMENT&lt;/name&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;description&gt;Deployment environment&lt;/description&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;defaultValue&gt;production&lt;/defaultValue&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;/hudson.model.StringParameterDefinition&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;/parameterDefinitions&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;/hudson.model.ParametersDefinitionProperty&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;/properties&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;definition class=\&quot;org.jenkinsci.plugins.workflow.cps.CpsFlowDefinition\&quot; plugin=\&quot;workflow-cps@2.94\&quot;&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;script&gt;
&quot; + &quot; pipeline &#123;
&quot; + &quot; agent any
&quot; + &quot; environment &#123;
&quot; + &quot; MAVEN_HOME = &#x27;/path/to/maven&#x27;
&quot; + &quot; DEPLOY_SERVER = &#x27;user@remote-server&#x27;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; parameters &#123;
&quot; + &quot; string(name: &#x27;BRANCH&#x27;, defaultValue: &#x27;main&#x27;, description: &#x27;Branch to build&#x27;)
&quot; + &quot; string(name: &#x27;ENVIRONMENT&#x27;, defaultValue: &#x27;production&#x27;, description: &#x27;Deployment environment&#x27;)
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; stages &#123;
&quot; + &quot; stage(&#x27;Checkout&#x27;) &#123;
&quot; + &quot; steps &#123;
&quot; + &quot; git branch: \&quot;$&#123;params.BRANCH&#125;\&quot;, url: &#x27;https://github.com/your-repo-url.git&#x27;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; stage(&#x27;Build&#x27;) &#123;
&quot; + &quot; steps &#123;
&quot; + &quot; sh &#x27;&#x27;&#x27;
&quot; + &quot; $&#123;MAVEN_HOME&#125;/bin/mvn clean package
&quot; + &quot; &#x27;&#x27;&#x27;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; stage(&#x27;Test&#x27;) &#123;
&quot; + &quot; steps &#123;
&quot; + &quot; sh &#x27;&#x27;&#x27;
&quot; + &quot; $&#123;MAVEN_HOME&#125;/bin/mvn test
&quot; + &quot; &#x27;&#x27;&#x27;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; stage(&#x27;Archive&#x27;) &#123;
&quot; + &quot; steps &#123;
&quot; + &quot; archiveArtifacts artifacts: &#x27;target/*.jar&#x27;, fingerprint: true
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; stage(&#x27;Deploy&#x27;) &#123;
&quot; + &quot; steps &#123;
&quot; + &quot; sshPublisher(
&quot; + &quot; publishers: [
&quot; + &quot; sshPublisherDesc(
&quot; + &quot; configName: &#x27;RemoteServer&#x27;,
&quot; + &quot; transfers: [
&quot; + &quot; sshTransfer(
&quot; + &quot; sourceFiles: &#x27;target/*.jar&#x27;,
&quot; + &quot; remoteDirectory: &#x27;/path/to/deploy&#x27;,
&quot; + &quot; removePrefix: &#x27;target&#x27;
&quot; + &quot; )
&quot; + &quot; ],
&quot; + &quot; usePromotionTimestamp: false,
&quot; + &quot; useWorkspaceInPromotion: false
&quot; + &quot; )
&quot; + &quot; ]
&quot; + &quot; )
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; post &#123;
&quot; + &quot; always &#123;
&quot; + &quot; emailext(
&quot; + &quot; to: &#x27;your-email@example.com&#x27;,
&quot; + &quot; subject: \&quot;Build: $&#123;currentBuild.fullDisplayName&#125;\&quot;,
&quot; + &quot; body: \&quot;Status: $&#123;currentBuild.result&#125;\nBuild URL: $&#123;env.BUILD_URL&#125;\&quot;
&quot; + &quot; )
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &#125;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;/script&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;sandbox&gt;true&lt;/sandbox&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;/definition&gt;
&quot; + &quot; &lt;triggers/&gt;
&quot; + &quot;&lt;/flow-definition&gt;&quot;; // 创建或更新 Job if (jenkins.getJob(jobName) != null) &#123; jenkins.updateJob(jobName, jobConfigXml); System.out.println(&quot;Job updated successfully!&quot;); &#125; else &#123; //true覆盖重名的 jenkins.createJob(jobName, jobConfigXml, true); System.out.println(&quot;Job created successfully!&quot;); &#125;&#125; 相关配置有三种模式： 1.freestyle 特征 2.maven 特征 3.flow 特征 踩坑： ​ 多git配置需要下载插件，也可以写脚本 ​ 缺少依赖就按照提示一个一个添加 1、关闭Jenkins https://gitlab.com/firstgroup2644947/cyis.green.ty.be.git 只需要在访问jenkins服务器的网址url地址后加上exit。例如我jenkins的地址http://127.0.0.1:8080/，那么我只需要在浏览器地址栏上敲下http://127.0.0.1:8080/exit 网址就能关闭jenkins服务. 2、重启Jenkies http://127.0.0.1:8080/restart 3、重新加载配置信息 http://127.0.0.1:8080/reload
